## Example environment variables (Monetag)
# Copy this file to .env.local for local development. For production, set
# the values in Vercel → Project Settings → Environment Variables instead.

# Monetag configuration (example placeholders):
# VITE_AD_PROVIDER=monetag
# VITE_MONETAG_ENABLED=true
# VITE_MONETAG_DOMAIN=5gvci.com
# VITE_MONETAG_ZONE_ID=11076770
# VITE_MONETAG_ZONE_1=11076796
# VITE_MONETAG_ZONE_2=244413

# Note: The previous Adsterra variables were removed because embedding raw
# third-party script HTML in environment variables may cause runtime errors
# during SSR or break builds. Use the Monetag zone IDs and the Monetag
# service worker approach instead.
